 also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Sir. Robert Sherborne Knight was born in 1271, his father, John Sherborn, was 21 and his mother, Mrs. John de Sherborne, was 19. He had at least 1 daughter. He died in 1342, at the age of 71."},"et":{"1271–1342":"1271–1342","1314–Female":"1314–Surnud","1251–Male":"1251–Surnud","1253–Female":"1253–Surnud","1314":"1314","1342":"1342","1253":"1253","1251":"1251","1271":"1271"},"fi":{"1271–1342":"1271–1342","1314–Female":"1314–Kuollut","1251–Male":"1251–Kuollut","1253–Female":"1253–Kuollut","1314":"1314","1342":"1342","1253":"1253","1251":"1251","1271":"1271"},"fr":{"1271–1342":"1271–1342","1314–Female":"1314–Décédée","1251–Male":"1251–Décédé","1253–Female":"1253–Décédée","1314":"1314","1342":"1342","1253":"1253","1251":"1251","1271":"1271","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Sir. Robert Sherborne Knight est né en 1271, son père, John Sherborn, avait 21 ans et sa mère, Mrs. John de Sherborne, avait 19 ans. Il a eu au moins 1 fille. Il est décédé en 1342, à l’âge de 71 ans."},"de":{"1271–1342":"1271–1342","1314–Female":"1314–Verstorben","1251–Male":"1251–Verstorben","1253–Female":"1253–Verstorben","1314":"1314","1342":"1342","1253":"1253","1251":"1251","1271":"1271","lifeSummary":"Als Sir. Robert Sherborne Knight 1271 geboren wurde, war sein Vater John Sherborn 21 und seine Mutter Mrs. John de Sherborne 19. Er hatte mindestens 1 Tochter. Er starb 1342 im Alter von 71 Jahren."},"ht":{"1271–1342":"1271–1342","1314–Female":"1314–Desede","1251–Male":"1251–Desede","1253–Female":"1253–Desede","1314":"1314","1342":"1342","1253":"1253","1251":"1251","1271":"1271"},"hu":{"1271–1342":"1271–1342","1314–Female":"1314–elhunyt","1251–Male":"1251–elhunyt","1253–Female":"1253–elhunyt","1314":"1314","1342":"1342","1253":"1253","1251":"1251","1271":"1271"},"id":{"1271–1342":"1271–1342","1314–Female":"1314–Telah Meninggal","1251–Male":"1251–Telah Meninggal","1253–Female":"1253–Telah Meninggal","1314":"1314","1342":"1342","1253":"1253","1251":"1251",